QuickTour Installation instructions

Prerequisites:
A MySQL Database with 3 tables:
  A user table with this structure: name (VARCHAR), salt (VARCHAR), digest (VARCHAR)
    The digest is encrypted with PHP's crypt function
  A poi table with this structure: id (INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT), lat (FLOAT), lng (FLOAT), place (VARCHAR), infoimg (VARCHAR), url (VARCHAR)
  A paths table with this structure: id (INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT), poi1 (INT NOT NULL), poi2 (INT NOT NULL), elnum (INT NOT NULL), lat (FLOAT), lng (FLOAT)
PHP with file writing permissions
A working web server

